{"tid":2505901,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"睇完Error遊，我原諒保錡？","createTime":"2021-04-27T03:24:53.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-27T03:35:42.000Z","uid":32051,"like":7,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"559e9449cc826d2d3c9a888714d6a4148bcbc9bd","tid":2505901,"uid":32051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T03:24:53.000Z","msg":"其實你班冚家產是否傻閪？<br />\n<br />\n咁如果我翻睇完獎門人，係咪就要原諒曾志偉條淫棍？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講好笑，受歡迎，輯數之多，獎門人一定唔會輸俾error遊。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果你話睇返一個舊嘅節目，你覺得果個賤人表現幾好，因為一個咁撚好笑嘅理由就可以原諒一條賤人嘅話。<br />\n<br />\n咁大家係咪應該原諒咗曾志偉先？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雙重標準到人格人品都唔理，盲撐夠件垃圾保錡未？"},{"pid":"0327a38621bb83eb4503909e4da6b8bab95d26a0","tid":2505901,"uid":57462,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T03:26:01.000Z","msg":"因為at the end of the day，某個藝人偷食邊個根本唔關連登仔事，只要個藝人entertain 到連登仔"},{"pid":"1f52e0e10be3428a393fdfd5e9ac660bd248f79b","tid":2505901,"uid":318980,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T03:26:30.000Z","msg":"唔會<br />\n好笑唔係因為曾志偉<br />\n係因為上去玩果班人"},{"pid":"6182778451bce8afd842825238714d7be6452e31","tid":2505901,"uid":191633,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T03:26:33.000Z","msg":"我份人好簡單，純粹覺得佢個樣咁醜仲聲大夾惡屌fans就唔值得原諒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c2d7fe64215d48f8e13cb4f17f8ff676dec6b09","tid":2505901,"uid":62891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T03:27:03.000Z","msg":"有佢就唔撚睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c542f4010c56bb2ac420046e61ee38faefeeacc","tid":2505901,"uid":62,"like":0